velocity: [-0.302733, 0.953075]  To create a  MagneticParticle  simply provide the constructor with one more number, the angular velocity:  ω   =   0.5  mp   =   MagneticParticle ( x0 ,   y0 ,   φ0 ,   ω )   MagneticParticle{Float64}
